Izolo bekulindeleke ukuthi iNkantolo eNkulu yaseMgungundlovu ikhiphe isinqumo ecaleni likaMnuz Nkosinathi Shangase (47), okuthiwa wabulala inkosikazi yakhe, uNkk Thabisile Shangase, uMaDoyisa. UNkk Shangase wabulawa ngo-Ephreli 2016. Ijaji obekumele likhiphe isinqumo belingakaqedi ukuhlanganisa umbiko walo, icala lase lihlehliselwa uLwesibili. Lo nesi kusolwa ukuthi wadutshulwa ngesibhamu i-R5. Umyeni wakhe, owayesebenza ophikweni lwePublic Order Policing (POP) eMgungundlovu, kuthiwa wayekade ehilizisene nenkosikazi yakhe eyayisafake umfaniswano wasemsebenzi. Kuthiwa wayidubulela phambi kwezingane zabo. Ilungu lo mndeni wenkosikazi lithe belilindele ukuthi inkantolo imlahle ngecala uShangase bese egwetshwa ngesenzo sakhe. Kwelinye icala, uMnuz Simphiwe Ndlela (40) waKwaDambuza, eMgungundlovu, uvele enkantolo yaseMgungundlovu ngecala lokubulala uninakhulu. Lihlehliselwe uMashi 5 ukuze kuqedwe ukuqoqa ubufakazi. UNdlela usagcinwe esitokisini. UNdlela kuthiwa wabulala uninakhulu, uNkk Judith Ndlela (90). Waboshwa ngoLwesine ilanga icala elenziwa ngalo. UNksz Thandeka Ndlela, okhulume neSolezwe ngeledlule emuva kwesehlo, uthe wayelele noninakhulu ngesikhathi uNdlela engqongqoza ngesankahlu lapho ababelele khona. Uthe wagcina engenile, elokhu eshisa impepho ekhuluma into engazwakali. Uthe esenza ukudla kwasekuseni, wezwa uninakhulu esekhala, ebhokodwa wuNdlela ngommese. UNksz Ndlela uthe waphuma eyocela usizo komakhelwane. Uthe wathi esebuya wafica uNdlela esebeke usawoti eduze kwesidumbu sikaninakhulu. Kuthiwa wayesika izicubu zakhe ezidla ziluhlaza.